{"TopicId":48044,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"Mod that categorises flights in tracking station?","CreatedByName":"TMS","CreatedById":57134,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-11T18:38:36Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"TMS","CreatedById":57134,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-11T18:38:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EDoes this exist?\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI get to about 15 flights and start wishing that I had some rudimentary ability to group flights into... well... groups.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EFor example, grouping comsat rings or the constituent parts of a planetary outpost.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EDo you know of anything like this?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mr Shifty","CreatedById":68146,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-11T21:25:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EYou can sort of achieve this. If you go to your vessel and right-click on the command pod, you can change the type of vessel: lander, station, pod, etc. These types can by sorted by using the existing tabs at the top of the tracking center.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stone Blue","CreatedById":77721,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-11T23:38:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EMaybe this?\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/46956-0-21-Targetron-Target-or-command-vessel-from-a-list-of-active-flights\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/46956-0-21-Targetron-Target-or-command-vessel-from-a-list-of-active-flights\u003C/a\u003E!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TMS","CreatedById":57134,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-12T09:10:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EYeah, I\u0027d seen that mod before. I think that\u0027s probably my best bet with its search ability.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EWhat I actually want is an additional field adding to the ships in the persistence file that allows me to set their group association.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EBasically, you should be able to somehow select multiple ships in the tracking station and \u0027collapse\u0027 them into a group name of your choosing, then be able to expand/view them at your convenience.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stone Blue","CreatedById":77721,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-12T17:14:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI agree. I usually start my new games with satellite constellations, and I find it kinda hard to believe there is no \u0022Satellite\u0022 type, yet there is a \u0022Flag\u0022 type...\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_rolleyes.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:rolleyes:\u0022\u003E...They either have to go as Ships or Stations...Which kind of clutters up THOSE two categories...Also makes the craft icons on the map screen almost useless... \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Mr Shifty\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Mr Shifty\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EThese types can by sorted by using the existing tabs at the top of the tracking center.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EYeah, but you can only choose one at a time, unless I am mistaken....Sometimes I want \u0022Ships\u0022 and just \u0022Stations\u0022...Or just \u0022Landers\u0022 and \u0022Ships\u0022 and \u0022Stations\u0022...\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EOh, and it would be nice to have a \u0022Base\u0022 category for planetary stations, instead of having to group them in with orbital stations... \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E ...i know you could put a flag at each base, and filter by \u0022Flag\u0022, but, eh..seems like a pain and unintuitive..??\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222013-10-12T17:20:41Z\u0022 title=\u002210/12/2013 05:20  PM\u0022 data-short=\u002210 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 12, 2013\u003C/time\u003E by Stone Blue\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SneakyGunz","CreatedById":111005,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-22T16:06:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI know this is a very old topic but I am surprised that nobody has made a folder/tab like mod to sort out the many many ships. Wishlisted!!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jas0n","CreatedById":57441,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-22T23:01:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223064241\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002248044\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221495469177\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022111005\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022SneakyGunz\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, SneakyGunz said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI know this is a very old topic but I am surprised that nobody has made a folder/tab like mod to sort out the many many ships. Wishlisted!!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTry this. also no one likes when you necro an old thread.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/81114-12-2016-10-28-haystack-continued-v0521/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Murdabenne","CreatedById":142825,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-23T02:51:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSometimes there are topics that deserve to be necro\u0027d?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SneakyGunz","CreatedById":111005,"CreatedDateTime":